### Blockchain API Endpoints (All endpoints working - Clean & Minimal)

### Step 1: Whitelist Target Address (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/admin/target-whitelist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetAddress": "0xee30E5b391aBf6Bf36a646FddfEaf256512d6B9D",
  "allowed": true
}

### Step 2: Create a Proposal (Requires 1 sETH balance)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "NEW PROPOSAL",
  "targetAddress": "0xee30E5b391aBf6Bf36a646FddfEaf256512d6B9D",
  "callData": "0x6a6f6577697a79"
}

### Step 3: Cast a Vote (Requires sETH balance for voting power)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/vote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 7,
  "support": true
}

### Get Proposal Details
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 7
}

### Get Proposal Votes
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 7
}

### Get Vote by User
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/vote-by-user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 1,
  "voter": "0xee30E5b391aBf6Bf36a646FddfEaf256512d6B9D"
}

### Execute Proposal (Only after voting period + delay)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 7
}

### Cancel Proposal
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 7
}

### Delete Expired Proposal
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/proposal/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proposalId": 7
} 